headline: 2026 Midstream/MLPs: Company-Level Tailwinds Amid Macro Clouds
summary: For the energy space, the 2026 outlook has arguably been an overhang for much of this year given concerns around oil prices and expectations for an oversupplied market in the new year.

headline: Is Targa Resources Stock Outperforming the Dow?
summary: Targa Resources has notably outperformed the Dow Jones Industrial Average in recent months, and analysts remain optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
